âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions (Using uv)
1ï¸âƒ£ Install uv
pip install uv


Or (recommended):

curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh


Verify:

uv --version

2ï¸âƒ£ Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/ashishwadhwani881/TMS_Backend.git
cd TMS_Backend/backend

3ï¸âƒ£ Create Virtual Environment & Install Dependencies
uv venv
source .venv/bin/activate      # Linux / macOS
.venv\Scripts\activate         # Windows

uv pip install -r requirements.txt


ğŸ“Œ uv automatically uses the virtual environment.

4ï¸âƒ£ Environment Variables

Create .env or settings/local.py:

DEBUG=True
SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key

5ï¸âƒ£ Run Migrations
uv run python manage.py makemigrations
uv run python manage.py migrate

6ï¸âƒ£ Create Superuser
uv run python manage.py createsuperuser

7ï¸âƒ£ Run Development Server
uv run python manage.py runserver


Server runs at:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/

